name: Fishing Boi Z
description:
Help the Fishing Boi explore the underground cavern. Fight your way through bats and cave crabs to be able to fish out 10 fish to escape! This is my first game made In the Godot engine. I started learning the engine the day the Jam started. It has been stressful but really fun!

A/D - Move left and right

Space - Jump

F - At a pond starts a fishing mini game

E - Attack and controls the bobber during the minigame

During the fishing mini game press E to bounce the bobber up. Keep it matched up with the fish to fill the progress bar.
